## 📈 Scalability Checkpoints

### At 10 Customers (₹9,990 MRR) - Week 3-4
**Status**: Break-even achieved
* **Action**: None. Monitor and optimize existing pipeline
* **Red Flags**:
  - If generation time >5 minutes: Upgrade Render Worker to Standard
  - If error rate >5%: Add automated retry logic in n8n
  - If churn >20% in first month: Emergency feedback calls

### At 25 Customers (₹24,975 MRR) - Month 2
**Status**: Profitability (covers time + costs)
* **Infrastructure**:
  - Review Render Worker performance, upgrade to Standard ($25/mo) if needed
  - Add automated retries for failed generations in n8n
  - Implement daily PostgreSQL backups to B2
* **Operations**:
  - Hire VA for customer support (₹10k/mo)
  - Create customer onboarding doc/video
  - Set up automated "Day 7 check-in" WhatsApp messages
* **Red Flags**:
  - If Render credits depleting faster than expected: Review per-video costs
  - If support taking >2 hours/day: Hire VA immediately

### At 50 Customers (₹49,950 MRR) - Month 3-4
**Status**: Sustainable business
* **Infrastructure**:
  - Consider upgrading to Cloudflare R2 instead of B2 for faster delivery
  - Add CDN for video delivery
  - Review n8n execution limits, may need Pro plan (₹4,200/mo)
* **Product**:
  - Build simple admin dashboard for customer self-service
  - Add top 3 requested features from feedback loop
  - Implement automatic monthly usage reports
* **Marketing**:
  - Allocate ₹15k/mo for paid ads (Meta/Google)
  - Test referral program (₹500 credit per successful referral)
* **Red Flags**:
  - If n8n hitting execution limits: Upgrade to Pro immediately
  - If queue delays >30 minutes: Add second Render Worker

### At 100 Customers (₹99,900 MRR) - Month 5-6
**Status**: Scaling phase
* **Infrastructure**:
  - Migrate to dedicated infrastructure (consider AWS/GCP)
  - Implement proper load balancing
  - Add Redis Cluster for distributed job queue
* **Team**:
  - Hire full-time customer success manager
  - Hire part-time developer for feature development
* **Product**:
  - Build customer dashboard with login
  - Add analytics and scheduling features
  - Consider white-label options for agencies

