## ⚠️ Risk Management
| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **API Cost Spike** | High | [cite_start]Set hard monthly spend caps in Replicate ($100) and Anthropic ($50) dashboards[cite: 124]. Monitor daily via admin dashboard. |
| **n8n Breakdown** | High | [cite_start]Sentry monitoring + 6-hourly cron health checks[cite: 124]. Keep backup webhook URL. |
| **Customer Churn** | Medium | [cite_start]Execute the Week 5 feedback loop and Day 7/Day 25 check-ins[cite: 124]. |
| **Image Quality** | Medium | [cite_start]Maintain a style library and perform human review in v1[cite: 124]. |
| **Render Credits Depletion** | Medium | Set alert at $400 usage. Budget for $31/mo after credits run out. |
| **Performance Degradation** | High | Track generation time per video. Upgrade Worker if >5min average. |

### 🚨 Performance Red Flags (Week 1 Testing)
Watch for these during Days 5-6 testing:
* **FFmpeg takes >3 minutes per video**: Render Worker is undersized, upgrade to Standard
* **Replicate costs >₹300/day during testing**: Runaway generation loops, check n8n retry logic
* **Total generation time >5 minutes**: Identify bottleneck and optimize
* **Error rate >5%**: Review error logs, add better error handling

